body_html:
@physicsai are you using compatible versions of this file and the pip package?

If you have tensorflow 0.12.0rc0 installed, you need to use the version of the file in r0.12 branch of this repo. If you have built tensorflow from source, you can use this file.

Also, please reach out to us by either filing an issue, or through stackoverflow. Pull requests, after merging, cannot really address any questions anymore.
